  "texts": [
    "Uni-MoE SettingsThe Uni-MoE's architectural specifications are presented inTable 1, exhibited along with the recently proposed MoE-LLaVA.",
    "Our exploration is anchored on scaling the Uni-MoE model, which is based on the LLaMA-7B architecture.",
    "The design and optimization of Uni-MoE are guided by specialized training tasks listed in Table 2.",
    "These tasks are instrumental in refining the capabilities of the MLP layers, thereby leveraging their specialized knowledge for enhanced model performance.",
    "We undertake eight single-modality expert tasks to elucidate the differential impacts of various training methodologies."
  ]
}